Available Tools: get_temperature | get_humidity | get_wind_speed | get_uv_index
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "unit": "celsius|fahrenheit" }
Response Schema: { "value": number, "unit": "string", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: What is the current humidity in Miami?
Call: { "func_call": "get_humidity", "location": "Miami", "unit": "celsius" }
Response: { "value": 78, "unit": "%", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T14:30:00Z" }

Question: Check the wind speed in Chicago right now.
Call: { "func_call": "get_wind_speed", "location": "Chicago", "unit": "celsius" }
Response: { "value": 18.5, "unit": "km/h", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T14:30:00Z" }

